00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:05.290
Brush your teeth with nothing using colorless
flavorless Nihilist Toothpaste.

00:00:05.290 --> 00:00:11.040
After eating a delicious bag of Chirps - the
protein-rich snack made out of beans, rice

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:12.150
and crickets.

00:00:12.150 --> 00:00:15.990
Because it’s episode 46 of LÜT.

00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:21.740
Wake up dressed in your bed with the wearable
futon air mattress and then strap on a pair

00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:23.800
of RocketSkates.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:29.640
Electric motorized skates that fit with almost
any shoe and allow you to go up to 12 MPH.

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:34.280
They’re controlled by tilting your feet
which means they’re hands free - great news

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:37.370
for anyone with giant lobster claws.

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:42.399
For hermit crabs looking to upgrade their
digs glassshell.com sells hand blown glass

00:00:42.399 --> 00:00:48.350
shells - which are made to accommodate the
contours of a crab’s exoskelton-y body.

00:00:48.350 --> 00:00:53.649
Snap together a Gummy Bear’s skeleton which
features detachable organs and a removable

00:00:53.649 --> 00:00:57.070
skullcap to see the Gummy Bear brain.

00:00:57.070 --> 00:01:02.199
Get grumpy thoughts out of your brain and
onto the pages of a grump notebook - a set

00:01:02.199 --> 00:01:06.750
of three including daily disappointments,
things that annoy me and fresh rants.

00:01:06.750 --> 00:01:12.670
To smell fresh and stay organized use Shower
Squids that hold shampoo and soap bottles

00:01:12.670 --> 00:01:17.000
and for something smelly that holds pretty
much anything there’s orange cream scented

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.030
Duck Tape.

00:01:18.030 --> 00:01:22.810
Tape together your own cardboard mask by following
instructions from Wintercroft.

00:01:22.810 --> 00:01:30.460
Download a PDF of plans to transform recycled
boxes into a 3D cat, owl or Stormtrooper.

00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:35.439
Then check out your new face in the Lucid
Mirror which contains a luminous 3D image

00:01:35.439 --> 00:01:38.750
of celestial clouds hanging in the reflection.

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:43.710
Hang beer and save space in the fridge with
bottleLoft - the world’s first magnetic

00:01:43.710 --> 00:01:46.070
bottle hanger for your fridge.

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:50.430
If you’re more of a milk drinker light up
your lactose using the glass of milk light

00:01:50.430 --> 00:01:55.430
that perfectly pairs with midnight cookie
dunking sessions courtesy of Dunkin’ Buddy.

00:01:55.430 --> 00:02:00.189
A device that saves dunked cookies from breaking
and getting lost in your cup.

00:02:00.189 --> 00:02:01.259
Pizza Smelly Pen.

00:02:01.259 --> 00:02:02.420
Pancakes Smelly Pen.

00:02:02.420 --> 00:02:03.870
Cotton Candy Smelly Pen.

