Ubi is an always-on voice-activated computer
that you simply plug in and talk to and it

00:02:09.410 --> 00:02:14.360
does the following: Voice-enabled internet
search, speakerphone, home speaker system,

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:19.640
voice memos, virtual assistant, alarm clock,
intercom, baby monitor, thermostat, and noise

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:21.000
pollution monitor.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:25.510
So for just one example if you’re baking
you can say, "OK Ubi..remind me in 20 minutes

00:02:25.510 --> 00:02:29.830
to take the cake out of the oven” and Ubi
is pretty much like okay cool no problem human

00:02:29.830 --> 00:02:31.520
I got this because I am Ubi.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.420
And this is an Indiana Jones cat bridge.

