show up on your doorstep that contains anything

00:02:43.740 --> 00:02:47.870
from do-it-yourself sushi candy to vanilla
ice cream Kit Kats.

00:02:47.870 --> 00:02:52.760
Then give yourself a break from cheap razors
and shave like a barber with the Beluga Razor.

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:57.540
A single edge exposed blade housed in premium
stainless steel that lets you shave like an

00:02:57.540 --> 00:02:59.110
old school barber.

00:02:59.110 --> 00:03:01.940
Shave yourself from Jaws with this Shark Repellent.

00:03:01.940 --> 00:03:05.830
And start the countdown on your Time Bomb
Kitchen Timer because we’re almost ready

00:03:05.830 --> 00:03:11.220
to ride off into the sunset on a motorized
monocycle - but make sure you remember that

00:03:11.220 --> 00:03:13.790
zombies give the best free hugs.

00:03:13.790 --> 00:03:15.650
